<lb n="1383b07" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="1383b08" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 2882</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="1383b09" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="1383014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】大英博物館藏燉煌本, S. 418, 【甲】大英博物館藏燉煌本, S2<unclear/>17, 甲本首缺</note>佛說呪魅經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="1383b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1383b11" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT85p1383b1101">爾時，佛在舍衛國妙龍□□□□□□□切眾
<lb n="1383b12" ed="T"/>生：「作罪不可論盡，□□□□□□□道令得開
<lb n="1383b13" ed="T"/>悟，吾<note n="1383015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以上甲本缺</note>今為汝說過去、未來之見。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1383b1313" rend="inline">「往昔空王
<lb n="1383b14" ed="T"/>佛時，給孤獨園中有一老，狐穴前燒其脂火，
<lb n="1383b15" ed="T"/>夜半日月五星下造作魅蠱，上牽天神，<note n="1383016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔下牽〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383016"><lem wit="【大】">下牽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="1383b16" ed="T"/>五帝，復牽山神，復牽河伯將軍，復牽五道大
<lb n="1383b17" ed="T"/>神，呼取百鬼造作魅蠱。或作蒲人，或作人形
<lb n="1383b18" ed="T"/>像，或作符書厭禱呪詛，或取人姓字，或取棘
<lb n="1383b19" ed="T"/>針，或<note n="1383017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">果＝裹【甲】</note><app n="1383017"><lem wit="【大】">果</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">裹</rdg></app>黃土，或向日月獨語不自覺知。或
<lb n="1383b20" ed="T"/>取人家衣裳，或取人衣帶，或取五綵綖縷，或
<lb n="1383b21" ed="T"/>取人家甑帶，或取人家瓫𤬪瓦器，或取人家
<lb n="1383b22" ed="T"/><note n="1383018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔驢馬牛羊〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383018"><lem wit="【大】">驢、馬、牛、羊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、<note n="1383019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猪＋（羊雞）【甲】</note><app n="1383019"><lem wit="【大】">猪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">猪羊雞</rdg></app>、狗毛，或取人家五<note n="1383020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行作具＝形之事【甲】</note><app n="1383020"><lem wit="【大】">行作具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">形之事</rdg></app>，或
<lb n="1383b23" ed="T"/>取人家門<note n="1383021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">楔＝簟【甲】</note><app n="1383021"><lem wit="【大】">楔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">簟</rdg></app>，或取人家匙箸作魅蠱；或<note n="1383022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奇＝騎【甲】</note><app n="1383022"><lem wit="【大】">奇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">騎</rdg></app>
<lb n="1383b24" ed="T"/>麻鄒馬，或刺人身，或<note n="1383023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">刺＝針【甲】</note><app n="1383023"><lem wit="【大】">刺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">針</rdg></app>人心<note n="1383024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔胎〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383024"><lem wit="【大】">胎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，或<note n="1383025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">計＝針【甲】</note><app n="1383025"><lem wit="【大】">計</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">針</rdg></app>人
<lb n="1383b25" ed="T"/>手脚，或針<note n="1383026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="1383026"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>眼孔，或針<app type="star" corresp="#1383026"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>腰背；或取人
<lb n="1383b26" ed="T"/>頭毛，或取黃土，或取五綵帛，或取人上、下衣
<lb n="1383b27" ed="T"/>帶，或魅蠱人田<note n="1383027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">苗＝作【甲】</note><app n="1383027"><lem wit="【大】">苗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">作</rdg></app>，或捉群抄舉向壁獨語。
<lb n="1383b28" ed="T"/>或作狩形像，或作人頭形像，或作<note n="1383028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔魅等〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383028"><lem wit="【大】">魅等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>符
<lb n="1383b29" ed="T"/>書厭禱呪咀，或<note n="1383029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔令〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383029"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>作人形言說不以道理。
<lb n="1383b30" ed="T"/><note n="1383030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＋（作）【甲】</note><app n="1383030"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">或作</rdg></app>魅蠱<note n="1383031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＋（田或魅蠱人）【甲】</note><app n="1383031"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">人田或魅蠱人</rdg></app>家牛、<note n="1383032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">馬羊犬＝羊犬馬【甲】</note><app n="1383032"><lem wit="【大】">馬、羊、犬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羊犬馬</rdg></app>、<note n="1383033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔雞猪狗〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383033"><lem wit="【大】">雞、猪、狗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，或作生
<pb n="1383c" ed="T" xml:id="T85.2882.1383c"/>
<lb n="1383c01" ed="T"/>人口舌，或作馬形，或作鬼神形，或作牛、羊、
<lb n="1383c02" ed="T"/><note n="1383034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔猪狗〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383034"><lem wit="【大】">猪、狗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>形。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1383c0204" rend="inline">「造<note n="1383035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魅之＝作魅【甲】</note><app n="1383035"><lem wit="【大】">魅之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">作魅</rdg></app>人，生死無道，強殺良善。
<lb n="1383c03" ed="T"/><note n="1383036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＋（自作若）【甲】</note><app n="1383036"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">若自作若</rdg></app>教他作，千殃萬罪，造者自當三梁六柱，
<lb n="1383c04" ed="T"/>還著本主，萬罪殃還自滅亡，急去三千六百
<lb n="1383c05" ed="T"/><note n="1383037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一十〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383037"><lem wit="【大】">一十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>里，止不得久停。今請東方青帝神王來
<lb n="1383c06" ed="T"/>食魅人腹，<note n="1383038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今請西方…頭）十三字∞（今請南方…眼）十三字【甲】</note><note n="1383038" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->（今請西方…頭）十三字∞（今請南方…眼）十三字【甲】</note>今請<note n="1383039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西方…請〕十三字－【甲】</note><note n="1383039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔西方…頭〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383039" cb:word-count="11"><lem wit="【大】">西方白帝神王來食魅人
<lb n="1383c07" ed="T"/>頭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，<note n="1383040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今請西方…頭）十三字∞（今請南方…眼）十三字【甲】</note><note n="1383040" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->〔今請〕－【甲】，（今請西方…頭）十三字∞（今請南方…眼）十三字【甲】</note><app n="1383040"><lem wit="【大】">今請</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>南方赤帝神王來食魅人<note n="1383041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眼＝腸【甲】</note><app n="1383041"><lem wit="【大】">眼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">腸</rdg></app>，今請
<lb n="1383c08" ed="T"/>北方黑帝神王來食<note n="1383042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魅＝媚【甲】</note><app n="1383042"><lem wit="【大】">魅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">媚</rdg></app>人<note n="1383043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">脚＝眼【甲】</note><app n="1383043"><lem wit="【大】">脚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">眼</rdg></app>，今請中央<note n="1383044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皇＝黃【甲】</note><app n="1383044"><lem wit="【大】">皇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">黃</rdg></app>
<lb n="1383c09" ed="T"/>帝神王來食魅人手。」</p><p xml:id="pT85p1383c0909" rend="inline">爾時，眾中有一菩薩名
<lb n="1383c10" ed="T"/>為大力，<note n="1383045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">整衣＝自正衣服【甲】</note><app n="1383045"><lem wit="【大】">整衣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">自正衣服</rdg></app>為佛作禮，白佛言：「世尊！弟子不
<lb n="1383c11" ed="T"/>解罪福，見世間眾生，多有五逆不信首道，共
<lb n="1383c12" ed="T"/>相<note n="1383046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魚肉有＝漁食【甲】</note><app n="1383046"><lem wit="【大】">魚肉有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">漁食</rdg></app><note n="1383047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＋（有）【甲】</note><app n="1383047"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">常有</rdg></app>惡念，不知生天堂受樂，不知
<lb n="1383c13" ed="T"/>有地獄憂苦，共相煎煮魅<note n="1383048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠱＝故【甲】</note><app n="1383048"><lem wit="【大】">蠱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">故</rdg></app>良善。唯願世
<lb n="1383c14" ed="T"/>尊，乃為弟子分別解說，令得道迹度脫一切。」</p>
<lb n="1383c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p1383c1501">爾時，佛告大力菩薩：「汝今<note n="1383049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未＝得開【甲】</note><app n="1383049"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">得開</rdg></app>解，<note n="1383050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吾＋（今）【甲】</note><app n="1383050"><lem wit="【大】">吾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">吾今</rdg></app>為汝<note n="1383051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔等〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383051"><lem wit="【大】">等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="1383c16" ed="T"/>分別解說，<note n="1383052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汝今諦聽＝爾時佛言【甲】</note><app n="1383052"><lem wit="【大】">汝今諦聽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">爾時佛言</rdg></app>。吾遣四天王等<note n="1383053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝今【甲】</note><app n="1383053"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">今</rdg></app>下
<lb n="1383c17" ed="T"/>世間，療治百惡不得停止，急去千里可得免
<lb n="1383c18" ed="T"/>脫。呪曰：魅公字槃<note n="1383054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">永＝市【甲】</note><app n="1383054"><lem wit="【大】">永</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">市</rdg></app>都，魅母字槃石奴，今
<lb n="1383c19" ed="T"/>知汝姓字、知汝姓名，若作魅蠱<note n="1383055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383055"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>返受其殃。
<lb n="1383c20" ed="T"/>汝教他作身自滅亡。吾今請四天神王<note n="1383056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔來〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383056"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>錄
<lb n="1383c21" ed="T"/>魅<note n="1383057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383057"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>名字，吾今呪魅人頭破作七分，如<note n="1383058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">阿梨樹＝阿犁樹【甲】下同</note><app n="1383058"><lem wit="【大】">阿
<lb n="1383c22" ed="T"/>梨樹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">阿犁樹</rdg></app>枝；今當知汝姓名，急去他方，不得停止。</p>
<lb n="1383c23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p1383c2301">「今當請南無佛陀來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿
<lb n="1383c24" ed="T"/>梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1383c2404" rend="inline">「今當請四天<note n="1383059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大）＋龍【甲】</note><app n="1383059"><lem wit="【大】">龍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大龍</rdg></app>王來，呪魅人頭破作
<lb n="1383c25" ed="T"/>七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1383c2508" rend="inline">「今當<note n="1383060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">請＋（牛頭）【甲】</note><app n="1383060"><lem wit="【大】">請</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">請牛頭</rdg></app>阿傍來，呪魅<note n="1383061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＋（不得停止）【甲】</note><app n="1383061"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">人不得停止</rdg></app>
<lb n="1383c26" ed="T"/>頭破作七分，如阿梨樹枝，<note n="1383062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不得…枝〕二十四字－【甲】</note><note n="1383062a" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不得停止〕－【甲】</note><app n="1383062a"><lem wit="【大】">不得停止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1383c2615" rend="inline">「<note n="1383062b" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛有…枝〕二十字－【甲】</note><app n="1383062b" cb:word-count="20"><lem wit="【大】">佛有如
<pb n="1384a" ed="T" xml:id="T85.2882.1384a"/>
<lb n="1384a01" ed="T"/>是大神呪，此魅人頭破作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="1384a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p1384a0201">「今當請普賢菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿
<lb n="1384a03" ed="T"/>梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a0304" rend="inline">「今當請<note n="1384001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大智…請〕四十二字－【甲】</note><note n="1384001a" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大智…枝〕十八字－【甲】</note><app n="1384001a" cb:word-count="18"><lem wit="【大】">大智菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作
<lb n="1384a04" ed="T"/>七分，如阿梨樹枝。</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a0408" rend="inline">「<note n="1384001b" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔今當…枝〕二十一字－【甲】</note><app n="1384001b" cb:word-count="21"><lem wit="【大】">今當請更明菩薩來，呪魅人
<lb n="1384a05" ed="T"/>頭破作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a0511" rend="inline">「<note n="1384001c" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔今當請〕三字－【甲】</note><app n="1384001c"><lem wit="【大】">今當請</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>月光菩薩
<lb n="1384a06" ed="T"/>來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a0615" rend="inline">「今當請
<lb n="1384a07" ed="T"/>蒙光菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿梨樹
<lb n="1384a08" ed="T"/>枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a0802" rend="inline">「今當請火光菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，
<lb n="1384a09" ed="T"/>如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a0906" rend="inline">「今當請華光菩薩來，呪魅人頭
<lb n="1384a10" ed="T"/>破作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a1010" rend="inline">「今當請月明菩薩來，
<lb n="1384a11" ed="T"/>呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a1114" rend="inline">「今當請文
<lb n="1384a12" ed="T"/>光菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p>
<lb n="1384a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p1384a1301">「今當請龍光菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿
<lb n="1384a14" ed="T"/>梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a1404" rend="inline">「今當請明星菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作
<lb n="1384a15" ed="T"/>七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a1508" rend="inline">「今當請千陽菩薩來，呪魅
<lb n="1384a16" ed="T"/>人，頭破作七分，如阿梨樹<note n="1384002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枝＋（今當請勇力菩薩來呪魅人頭破作七分如阿犁樹枝）【甲】</note><app n="1384002"><lem wit="【大】">枝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">枝今當請勇力菩薩來呪魅人頭破作七分如阿犁樹枝</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a1612" rend="inline">「今當請普明菩
<lb n="1384a17" ed="T"/>薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a1716" rend="inline">「今當
<lb n="1384a18" ed="T"/>請大明菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿梨樹
<lb n="1384a19" ed="T"/><note n="1384003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枝＋（今當請轉輪菩薩來呪魅人頭破作七分如阿犁樹枝）【甲】</note><app n="1384003"><lem wit="【大】">枝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">枝今當請轉輪菩薩來呪魅人頭破作七分如阿犁樹枝</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a1902" rend="inline">「今當請同光菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，
<lb n="1384a20" ed="T"/>如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a2006" rend="inline">「<note n="1384004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔今當…枝〕二十一字－【甲】</note><app n="1384004" cb:word-count="21"><lem wit="【大】">今當請日中菩薩來，呪魅人頭
<lb n="1384a21" ed="T"/>破作七分，如阿梨樹枝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a2110" rend="inline">「今當請建立菩薩來，
<lb n="1384a22" ed="T"/>呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a2214" rend="inline">「今當請樹
<lb n="1384a23" ed="T"/>王菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p>
<lb n="1384a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p1384a2401">「今當請龍<note n="1384005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝王【甲】</note><app n="1384005"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">王</rdg></app>菩薩來，呪魅人頭破作七分，如
<lb n="1384a25" ed="T"/>阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a2505" rend="inline">「今當請地動菩薩來，呪魅人頭破
<lb n="1384a26" ed="T"/>作七分，如阿梨樹枝。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384a2609" rend="inline">「今當請東方青帝神王
<lb n="1384a27" ed="T"/>來，呪魅人不得停止。今當請南方赤帝神王
<lb n="1384a28" ed="T"/>來，呪魅人不得停止。今當請西方白帝神王
<lb n="1384a29" ed="T"/>來，呪魅人不得停止。今當請北方黑帝神王
<pb n="1384b" ed="T" xml:id="T85.2882.1384b"/>
<lb n="1384b01" ed="T"/>來，呪魅人不得停止。今當呼日月五星二十
<lb n="1384b02" ed="T"/>八宿來，攝魅人不得停止，急去千里。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384b0215" rend="inline">「東方大
<lb n="1384b03" ed="T"/><note n="1384006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狩＝獸【甲】</note><app n="1384006"><lem wit="【大】">狩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">獸</rdg></app>來食魅人身，南方蜈蚣來食魅人<note n="1384007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔眼西…人〕九字－【甲】</note><app n="1384007" cb:word-count="9"><lem wit="【大】">眼，西
<lb n="1384b04" ed="T"/>方白象來食魅人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>頭，北方黑象來<note n="1384008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">啄＝食【甲】</note><app n="1384008"><lem wit="【大】">啄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">食</rdg></app>魅人心
<lb n="1384b05" ed="T"/>藏，中央黃帝<note n="1384009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔神〕－【甲】</note><app n="1384009"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>龍王來食魅人神。</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384b0514" rend="inline">「吾見魅
<lb n="1384b06" ed="T"/>人眼目角張，或作猖狂不似人形，或在人門
<lb n="1384b07" ed="T"/>前，或<note n="1384010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＋（人）【甲】</note><app n="1384010"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">在人</rdg></app>屋裏，或在碓磨上，或在人田地間
<lb n="1384b08" ed="T"/>跳<note n="1384011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">良＝踉【甲】</note><app n="1384011"><lem wit="【大】">良</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">踉</rdg></app>不止。或正月歲日，或正月十五日，或
<lb n="1384b09" ed="T"/>時<note n="1384012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">節＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="1384012"><lem wit="【大】">節</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">節之</rdg></app>日，或燒其脂火、呪說不止：吾知汝<note n="1384013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姓＋（字知汝姓）【甲】</note><app n="1384013"><lem wit="【大】">姓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">姓字知汝姓</rdg></app>
<lb n="1384b10" ed="T"/>名，不得停止，急去他方。若坐<note n="1384014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滅亡若立＝坐喪若立倒地【甲】</note><app n="1384014"><lem wit="【大】">滅亡、若立</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">坐喪若立倒地</rdg></app>消滅，
<lb n="1384b11" ed="T"/>頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝。若生<note n="1384015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">赤＝人【甲】</note><app n="1384015"><lem wit="【大】">赤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">人</rdg></app>口、<note n="1384016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔赤〕－【甲】</note><app n="1384016"><lem wit="【大】">赤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>舌，
<lb n="1384b12" ed="T"/>菩薩呪令消滅，急去不得<note n="1384017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">久＝停【甲】</note><app n="1384017"><lem wit="【大】">久</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">停</rdg></app>留。」</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384b1213" rend="inline">爾時，世尊
<lb n="1384b13" ed="T"/><note n="1384018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（唱）＋言【甲】</note><app n="1384018"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唱言</rdg></app>：「我今告十方眾生等，吾<note n="1384019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今為＝語【甲】</note><app n="1384019"><lem wit="【大】">今為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">語</rdg></app>汝一切眾
<lb n="1384b14" ed="T"/>生<note n="1384020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（為）＋善【甲】</note><app n="1384020"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">為善</rdg></app>男子、善女人<note n="1384021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說此＝等造作【甲】</note><app n="1384021"><lem wit="【大】">說此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">等造作</rdg></app>呪魅經。時有十方諸
<lb n="1384b15" ed="T"/>佛、過去七佛、十六王子佛、天上諸菩薩、天人、
<lb n="1384b16" ed="T"/>羅漢、四天大王、天龍八部、諸善<note n="1384022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（鬼）＋神【甲】</note><app n="1384022"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鬼神</rdg></app>、四道果
<lb n="1384b17" ed="T"/>人，一會<note n="1384023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔在〕－【甲】</note><app n="1384023"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>須彌山頭龍華樹下，<note n="1384024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＝許【甲】</note><app n="1384024"><lem wit="【大】">平</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">許</rdg></app>量眾生
<lb n="1384b18" ed="T"/>云何可度？若有比丘、比丘尼、優婆塞、優婆夷、
<lb n="1384b19" ed="T"/>男子、女人，有能燒香禮佛，受持此經供養不
<lb n="1384b20" ed="T"/>絕，令人得福。若有憂苦之人能生善念，皆得
<lb n="1384b21" ed="T"/>天堂之樂。若有人轉此經時，先清潔身行道
<lb n="1384b22" ed="T"/>燒香受持可得度脫。若能誦此經七遍，呪魅
<lb n="1384b23" ed="T"/>頭破作七分如阿梨樹枝，<note n="1384025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（一切…會））十二字＝（（佛說此經已））五字【甲】</note><note n="1384025a" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一切…脫〕八字－【甲】</note><app n="1384025a" cb:word-count="8"><lem wit="【大】">一切眾苦皆悉解
<lb n="1384b24" ed="T"/>脫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT85p1384b2402" rend="inline"><note n="1384025b" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（爾時一會））四字＝（（佛說此經已））五字【甲】</note><app n="1384025b" cb:word-count="4"><lem wit="【大】">爾時，一會</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">佛說此經已</rdg></app>一切眾<note n="1384026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝會【甲】</note><app n="1384026"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">會</rdg></app>，聞經歡<note n="1384027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仰為佛＝喜【甲】</note><app n="1384027"><lem wit="【大】">仰，為佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">喜</rdg></app>作
<lb n="1384b25" ed="T"/>禮，<note n="1384028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔持念〕－【甲】</note><app n="1384028"><lem wit="【大】">持念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>奉行。</p>
<lb n="1384b26" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="1384029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋呪【甲】</note><app n="1384029"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">佛說呪</rdg></app>魅<note n="1384030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【甲】，此下甲本奧書曰令願進子一心供養</note><app n="1384030"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">經一卷</rdg></app><note n="1384030" place="foot" type="rest">此下甲本奧書曰令願進子一心供養</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>